Rule: Higher education (Masters, Doctorate, Bachelors, Prof-school) leads to higher income.
Sales, Professional, and White-Collar occupations lead to higher income.
Gender being Male leads to higher income.
Being Self-Employed leads to higher income.
More hours per week (significantly more) leads to higher income.
Age flexibility (younger or older) can still lead to higher income.
Gender flexibility (both male and female can lead to higher income under certain conditions).
